file: ToolCall.php
class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Domain\\Tool\\ToolCall"
type: readonly final class
summary: "Represents a discrete tool invocation within an agent's execution flow, capturing the identifier, target tool name, and serialized arguments. It serves as a value object to track the sequence and context of tool calls during runtime."
